      "comment": "BEAUTIFUL MAGPIE (8) last start finished 4th over 520m at Wentworth Park beaten 6 lengths (30.20) behind Magic Fletch in a Grade 4/5 on June 6. Can find winning form. SKEDADDLE ARLO (2) had a low draw last time over 630m at Nowra but was in traffic and fell. Key chance on best form. WRITTEN IN GOLD (1) has some solid form under his belt and proved too strong last time to win by half a length at this track in a handy 22.63 beating Desi's Dream. Reliable out of the boxes and should take advantage of the inside draw. Should be in this for a long way. TURBO HARRY (5) in the money here last time and looks a top-three prospect again.",
